guide.introduction:
Designing on your own Dorm Life at '''DIY Magazine'''

It's back to school time! Before you dive into schoolwork spend a little time making your dorm a bit homier. You won’t go wrong with these dorm room must-haves.

We all know those dorm rooms are a bit tight so stay organized and store your loose items in these creative flora fabric storage boxes.
